OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBright or sunny spells and
OL,6,Fshowers, the best of the sunnier
OL,7,Fperiods for Angus, Dundee and Fife
OL,8,Fduring the morning. The showers could
OL,9,Fbe heavy, perhaps the odd rumble of
OL,10,Fthunder.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA few bright spells this
OL,13,Fevening followed by a risk of further
OL,14,Fshowers, some of which may be heavy at
OL,15,Ffirst before dying out through the
OL,16,Frest of the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
