OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA mainly dry and partly cloudy
OL,6,Fmorning. Sunny intervals and showers
OL,7,Ffor the afternoon, the best of the dry
OL,8,Fand sunniest conditions on the east
OL,9,Fcoast.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FRain
OL,12,For showers on Tuesday and Wednesday,
OL,13,Foccasionally heavy at first. Drier on
OL,14,FThursday. Milder than of late,
OL,15,Fpotentially warm in brighter spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
